{\listtext	\'95	}Approximately 1 pound {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/sugar/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 granulated sugar}}\cf2  (about 2 cups)\cf0 \
